      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a total gem? I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, it is in stunning, like-new condition! It\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously cared for, and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents\u2014just pure perfection. I\u2019m so excited for someone else to get behind the wheel and enjoy this beauty. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
