      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade 2019 Porsche Macan S in pristine Jet Black Metallic. This vehicle has been fastidiously garage-kept and remains in showroom condition. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, with absolutely no stone chips, scratches, or door dings. The Agate Grey leather interior is flawless, showing no bolster wear or creasing, and retains its original factory scent. Mechanically, this car is perfect; it has a full documented service history from authorized dealerships, including a recent major service and brand-new Michelin Pilot Sport tires. Every button, feature, and sensor functions exactly as it did the day it was delivered. This is a turn-key opportunity for a buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
